00:01:38.220 --> 00:01:47.290
&gt;&gt;DAVID STEPHENSON: Thank you David, I really
appreciate it. So, today I'm going to give

00:01:47.290 --> 00:01:55.610
you an overview on my book, Data Dynamite.
