00:01:55.610 --> 00:02:05.730
particularly to Google's mission. But before
I get going I have admit a couple of things

00:02:05.730 --> 00:02:12.520
about myself. First of all, I was a religion
major in college. While I never had any intentions

00:02:12.520 --> 00:02:19.550
of becoming a minister I have become an evangelist.
